description.text:
Happy hacking cxxmas all you nerds, geeks, dorks and the 1337, with this Asambler C++laus... 
Of couse he is wearing a raspberry red jacket (may vary depending on you own filament) and drinking hot Java™ with cookies while carrying all the bits and hardware in his ARM® that you wanted... but only to good sudoers... And while he drives away in his sleigh, pulled by penguins, you hear him laugh &quot;RPN, Rudolph, RPN - 67, 67, 67&quot;
May we have lots of ICE and spice this winter, so that you can print some cool enclosures for new homemade gadgets.
